---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Tropic Wings Transfers"
  description="Privacy Policy for Tropic Wings Transfers — Cairns Airport to Port Douglas transfer service operated by Tropic Wings Cairns Tours & Charters."
  canonical="/privacy"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8 py-16">
    <nav class="text-on-surface-variant text-xs font-label mb-8 flex items-center gap-2">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Tropic Wings Transfers</a>
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">chevron_right</span>
      <span>Privacy Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-4xl font-headline font-black tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 font-body text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
        <p>Tropic Wings Transfers is operated by Tropic Wings Cairns Tours &amp; Charters Pty Ltd, ABN 123 456 789, 278 Hartley Street, Cairns QLD 4870, Australia. You can contact us at <a href="mailto:info@tropicwings.com.au" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@tropicwings.com.au</a> or +61 7 4041 9400.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">2. Information we collect</h2>
        <p>When you make a booking we collect: your name, email address, phone number, nationality, passenger names, flight details, and payment information. We do not store full card numbers — payment data is handled by our PCI-compliant payment processor.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">3. How we use your information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to process and confirm bookings, send booking confirmations and travel reminders, monitor flight arrivals for delay management, respond to customer service enquiries, and comply with legal obligations.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">4. Disclosure</h2>
        <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share data with our payment processor, flight monitoring services, and authorities where required by law.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">5. Data retention</h2>
        <p>Booking records are retained for 7 years for accounting and legal compliance purposes, then securely deleted.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">6. Your rights</h2>
        <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data by emailing <a href="mailto:info@tropicwings.com.au" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@tropicwings.com.au</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">7. Cookies</h2>
        <p>This site uses essential cookies only (session management). No advertising or tracking cookies are set.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-3">8. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The current version is always available at this URL.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
